PC Number Date Chapter Bill Dept
 2008-11752008-06-18,  INDUSTRY,  ,  , 
ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisAppointment by the Minister of Industry of WILLIAM C. WERRY of Edmonton, Alberta, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, representing the region set out in subparagraph 11(3)(a)(v) of the Act, to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of four years, in the place of Fay Orr.
